{"tid":201906,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為何總遇到渣男？美國研究「可能妳也是渣女」","createTime":"2017-04-15T06:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T15:00:32.000Z","uid":105678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dca76a0f9b21c943762de9f4dc317261d049e8fb","tid":201906,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"韓劇中的歐巴百百款，舉凡陽光型男、斯文暖男、粗獷霸氣的大男人等，都有各自擁戴的族群；但在生活中，女孩們是否選來選去都是同一種菜，或總是遇到渣男？科學研究顯示，人類在挑選伴侶時通常會「物以類聚」，所以如果都遇到渣人，自己也可能是個渣人！<br />\n<br />\n美國加州大學近日研究發現，超過1000對的異性戀情侶以及他們的前任，無論是認真戀愛或速食交往，他們在選擇伴侶時，通常都挑選跟自己有相同的特徵的人，例如是宗教背景、教育背景或是智商程度等。<br />\n<br />\n學者歸納後認為，這是因為人類的生活習慣使然，簡單來說，就是有吸引力的人，通常會選擇同樣有吸引力的人作為伴侶。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://fashion.ettoday.net/news/903106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffashion.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F903106&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=5af34cbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://fashion.ettoday.net/news/903106</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇吓叫春台班5P <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1591ae26617668dd3c0dfdabe8e70949861731b","tid":201906,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"要做研究先知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77425add85ccbd3c9f0d7f7fe584bfb042ce174","tid":201906,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T08:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要做研究先知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d6314c6260fd89245ecb9246dbbfc4e0143404","tid":201906,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要做研究先知?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />